            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Pure gold was readily available in 4 in.x4 in. sheets,",
                "~2.6 mg/cm2 thick, as dental gold foil. The gold",
                "target consisted of several thicknesses of this foil",
                "cut into a strip approximately 1cm by 8cm. It was",
